title: Class F
content:
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:jakstyle]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:centered-header-bhl]]
[[=]]
[[module rate]]
Please hold onto me whilst my world goes dark,
Little time will my mind be clear as day,
Soon my mind will be full of question-marks,
So hold me as it starts fading away

Attempt to build a mental Ark,
Write notes to stop neuronal slay,
Alas millions will disembark,
Memories never to replay

Smile in the local park,
Is it June or July,
Memories run like snark,
And I question why

Neuronal shock,
Faces won't stay,
Unknown o'clock,
I am okay

Walk? No,
Decry,
Embark,
More gray

Murk,
Bye,
Smirk,
Sky

[[/=]]
